```python
class ExampleEngine:
    def __init__(self, message_bus: MessageBus):
        self.message_bus = message_bus
        self.obs_bus = self.message_bus.get_observability_bus()
        self.context_manager = context_manager(self, message_bus)
        self.llm_manager = llm_manager(self, message_bus)
        self.tool_manager = default_tool_manager(self, message_bus)
        llm_manager.set_model("gpt-4o-mini")
        tool_manager.register_tools([get_weather, create_file, search_page])

    def execute(self, prompt: str) -> str:
        """Execute a prompt."""
        response = llm_manager.generate(prompt, tools=tools.compile(exclude=["search_page"]))
        if response.has_tool_calls():
            # execute all tool calls
            for tool_call in response.tool_calls:
                tool_result = self.tool_manager.execute_tool_call(tool_call)
                self.context_manager.add_tool_result(tool_call.id, tool_result)
            # close out the tool calls
            response = llm_manager.generate(context=self.context_manager.get_context())
        return response.content
```
